text.tspan: You are standing on a high plane.
There is a large tree in front of you.
There is a rickety old ladder under/leaning against the tree.
There are flowers next to the path to the north-west.
In the distance, you see a low plain.
The flowers are yellow and quite delightful.
The flowers smell like a wet dog.
The low plain is to the north-west.
There is a hut on the low plain with a large tree next to it.
The hut is on the low plain.
You can't see it very clearly from here.
Because it is too far away.
The mountain is huge and imposing.
There is a cloud at the top of the mountain.
You take the path to the north-west.
With a galliant roar, you set off down the path to the north-west .
